description: A distorted, pixelated image shows a building, trees, and a sign reading "OT CROSS."
A blurry, light cyan-colored image shows indistinct shapes and small dark specks.
People are partially visible behind a reddish-brown railing.
A blurry close-up shot shows the back and right arm of a person wearing a light-colored shirt with darker ruffled trim.
A grainy, purplish film image shows a crowd of people walking down a city street, some wearing shorts and other summer clothing.
A blurry, cyan-toned image shows a finish line and blurred figures, likely from a race or sporting event.
A blurry, reddish-tinted image shows people and vehicles on a city street, possibly during a parade or gathering.
A blurry, darkly lit image shows a group of people, some of whom appear to be children.
A blurry, heavily pixelated, and color-distorted image appears to show a crowd of people, some of whom may be dancing or moving rhythmically.
A white surface is sparsely speckled with small, dark blue spots and marks.
A solid blue screen is visible, with some small, faint scratches or dust particles.
A grainy, reddish film shows people carrying a banner that reads "GAY/LESBIAN RIDE DAY 10" at a parade.
A blurry, blue-toned image appears to show a crowd of people, some shirtless, behind a railing or fence.
A white background is lightly speckled with small, predominantly blue dots.
A blurry, grainy image shows a group of people in what appears to be a dimly lit room.
A blurry, low-quality image shows a group of people in a dark setting, with one person holding a sign that reads "ITN".
A blurry, magenta-tinted crowd of people is visible.
Two people wearing t-shirts, one with a hat, stand in a room.
Several shirtless men, one wearing a race bib with the number 1203, stand near large white containers.
A distorted image shows a wall with graffiti, including the partial words "LESBIAN" and "HUMAN."
A blurry, low-quality image shows parts of a baseball stadium, including a sign reading "STAMP OUT AIDS" and parts of two figures, possibly players.
A blurry, grainy image appears to show a person bending down behind bars, possibly in a jail cell.
A blurry, color-shifted image shows figures behind a railing or fence.
A blurry image shows a brick wall with signs reading "STAMP OUT AIDS" and "FU KHIS".
A blurry, distorted image shows a group of people in a dimly lit space, bathed in red and purple light.
The image shows a white background with small, sparsely scattered dark blue specks.
A blurry, purple-toned image shows figures and speckles, possibly dirt or damage to the film.
A blurry, color-distorted image appears to show part of a baseball field with bleachers in the background and a figure in the foreground.
A distorted, brightly colored abstract image is displayed, possibly a corrupted video still or digital art piece.
A blurry, distorted image shows a wall with posters that read "STAMP OUT AIDS" and "FLU KILLS" taped to it.
A digitally distorted image depicts a group of people on a busy street, with colorful, pixelated patterns overlaying the scene and text fragments visible.
A blurry, color-shifted image shows a person wearing a tank top with the number 1203 on it.
A group of people march in a parade, carrying banners that read "National Assoc. Black & White Men" and "Back and White Together-Men".
A blurry cyan image displays faded rectangular shapes and small dark specks.
A blurry, vintage-looking image shows a group of people, with a woman with brown hair in the foreground.
A blurry, distorted image shows a person wearing a tank top and dark pants standing behind a railing, with other figures and a fence visible in the background.
The image is entirely black.
Blurry figures wearing hats and sunglasses are visible in the frame.
A group of people, some shirtless and some wearing running clothes, stand behind a metal barricade.
